# Handlers

- Validate input at the boundary; return appropriate 4xx responses with a JSON error shape consistent with other handlers in this API.
- Respect cookie-based sessions and existing auth middleware patterns.

# Logging

- Use structured logging only where the codebase already does; add context (e.g. request identifiers) when matching local style.
- Never log secrets, session tokens, passwords, or full bodies that may contain credentials.
